The experiment flow is based on the scientifc method definition from the wikipedia:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scientific_method

The experiment flow will have the following steps, and no step will be available unless the previous one has been completed:
1.Question 
2.Hypothesis and Null Hypothesis
3.Experiment
3.1 Method
4.Analysis
5.Report

Propose change to format:
Aim 
Hypothesis
Method
Results (inc analysis)
Conclusion
Evaluation
(Standard format used in education at all levels here)
